Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不爽氣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的喜歡菈菈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不討厭菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那你就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你只不過是個優柔寡斷的廢柴而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟菈菈根本就不配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我把你跟地球一起毀滅掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了  為什麼要把地球也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這件事…絕對不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓大家…讓小春菜被你給殺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化成灰吧  螻蟻之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  求你別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要對梨斗做過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是爸爸嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不配做你的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事不是爸爸可以決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗是我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管誰說什麼  他都是我最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗是一個很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅可靠  而且不管什麼時候都在拚命努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗他  梨斗他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我最喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  戴比路克王這樣說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從回來了以後就一直關在房間裡不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為宇宙第一的男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為宇宙第一的男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}宇宙第一的  男人  男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,28)\fscx320}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙第一的男子漢麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那麼強的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是很難說得出口的台詞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底有哪些長處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中時倒是踢過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這次射門一定要完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要搭上我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的障壁可還要厚得多喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說宇宙第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連市內第一都做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  先去跑步好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,側腹好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是運動不足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜  為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧遇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  一大早就能遇到小春菜真是超好運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西連寺是帶狗出來散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量延長下去吧  這樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得必須有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  卻不知道該做些什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就先跑步看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為最近頹廢  一會就跑不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有所改變…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得心中的答案也一定能夠明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我喜歡的是小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣的話菈菈的事情就
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs22}是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這樣的情況下猶豫不決
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白自己很優柔寡斷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被菈菈父親的話說中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在自己能夠挺起胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白自己到底是怎樣的人以後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  才能夠得出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻很難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君的這點我也應該學習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以為你加油嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  可以為結城君而加油嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我差不多也該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了  馬隆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油是指…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  梨斗  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  別穿成那樣到處亂轉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…稍微是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  穿上衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  春菜早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個「大鏡」說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形式上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會談的記錄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小春菜真是積極呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大宅世代相繼  180歲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點像兩人間的秘密而有點讓人害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜也說了要為我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之加油看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是陪小狗散步順便的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻能和小春菜共度兩人獨處的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個  帥殿  並射之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,循先聖之意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直持續下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  因為下雨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說也下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得今天也一定會跑步的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也猶豫過的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週日也跑步嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…大概也會跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我  做好便當帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添麻煩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說沒有比這更值得感激的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超期待週日了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  這不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會的約定麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會  約會  約會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  感覺有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竊笑的表情啊  有什麼事情發生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是經常這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不快點的話就要遲到了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢？  春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒這事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要製作便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞了  真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是容易看透呢  春菜你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  稍微安心下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜該做的事也是會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜  注意到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  你稍微變開朗了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得必須有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能改變嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  練習持續還不到一週呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難為情的  能不能至少穿上內褲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來的話至少敲個門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是是  我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這邊才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道是不是好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以吃這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一粒米都那麼有咬勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面恰到好處的調味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放的是梅干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和米飯融為一體的這酸味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次嚼便會在口中擴散的這種旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直可以稱得上是飯團裡極品中的極品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更棒的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我頭一次吃上小春菜親手做的料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理啊  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:16:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是世界上最幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西連寺  你很擅長料理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有  我還在學習中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹雖然也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  之前你也見過的吧  美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  美柑很能幹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬隆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬隆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝  平安無事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是西連寺的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  不把衣服弄乾的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我家吧  就在附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下  我去放洗澡水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡水？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜一直在用的浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜就在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水溫合適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  正合適
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就幫你洗乾淨然後烘乾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然變成這樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我們家沒有可以替換的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你父母呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和姐姐兩個人一起住的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來這是姐姐租的房子  因為離學校比較近…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你姐姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和朋友一起出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…多麼可怕的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是20年前的劇情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那時候我還沒出生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是小春菜的房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中時候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是想擅自看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊  初中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  那時候猿山他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  十分熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君也表現得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…差不多衣服快要乾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  倒也不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜  我給你帶東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽  你這個混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了  偏偏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是廢柴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定已經被徹底討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是非常失落的表情  發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是經常這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我想去死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}魔法火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}要放一個大煙火了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}極限爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}fire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.82,0:23:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要增強體力的話  我有個好主意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛茲星的傳統儀式  銀河猩猩獵捕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.85,0:23:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼獵捕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說為了這個特意去宇宙是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  獵場是在地球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  為什麼地球上會有這種巨大生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步走錯的話  我們就會被獵殺掉  要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  To  LOVEる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密林的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且小春菜也一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.86,0:24:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把她捲到這種危險的事情裡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.64,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}水玉は愛され模様
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:15.31,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこだって生きてゆけるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:22.22,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大切な私のお守りよ　連れて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:26.27,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}旅をして君のもとまで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.83,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}波に乗ってぐんぐんどこまで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:37.27,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}水玉は言ったわ　愛するとは時に醜くもあると
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:44.17,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}踏み出す足　小さく震える地面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:54.40,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}答えなど要らない　この想い消えないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:59.30,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星にララバイ　歌ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.94,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君とバイバイ　できるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:10.14,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘯いた空　嘘つきどこ？　水玉と目が合った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:13.74,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今ララバイ　歌ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:19.04,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君とバイバイ　できるはずはないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:25.86,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い乗せ　君に届くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:10.26,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星にララバイ　歌ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:15.31,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君とバイバイ　できるはずはないでしょう
